      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just left the dealership for the first time. The paint is flawless, the interior is pristine, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping it perfect, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
