    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior maintains its original factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently enhanced by a professional multi-stage ceramic coating. There are no dings, swirl marks, or stone chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is impeccable; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one, and the interior still carries a fresh scent. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the advanced driver assistance systems, operates perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. I possess a complete, chronological service binder documenting every oil change and inspection. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full transmission service and a fresh set of high-performance tires. It drives with the same precision and tightness as the day it was first delivered. This is a no-excuses vehicle for someone who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 43900.0,
